      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> red Thai curry paste</strong>, <strong>ginger paste</strong> and <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>to the pan and cook for 1 min further or until fragrant</p>",
