    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Thai-style beef mince rice with mangetout </strong>and garnish with the <strong>reserved chopped basil</strong>, a <strong>lime wedge</strong> and <strong>remaining chilli flakes </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
